title: KUT from the Kloth Women's Kelsey High-Rise Ankle Flare with Raw Hem in Optic White
description: LAID-BACK WITH THE PERFECT AMOUNT OF EDGE, THE KELSEY IS CROPPED WITH JUST THE RIGHT AMOUNT OF FLARE. The kelsey is fitted through the hips and thighs and finishes off with a cropped kick flare for a modern take on the classic silhouette.

Look modern and stylish effortlessly by wearing KUT from the Kloth Kelsey High-Rise Ankle Flare with Raw Hem in Optic White pants. They feature regular fit, cropped legs, high-rise waist, and classic five pocket style. A front zip-fly with button closure makes the pants perfect in fit. Stretchable in design, the pants are fitted through the hips and thighs and finishes off with a cropped kick flare for a modern take on the classic silhouette. 98% cotton, 2% spandex. Machine washable.
